UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2602
1 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
2 Kentucky:
3 Section 1. The members of the Senate honor the extraordinary life and
4 centennial milestone of Geraldine "Bubby" Litvin Shaffer and wish her continued joy
5 surrounded by family and community.
6 Section 2. When the Senate adjourns this day, it does so in honor and
7 recognition of Geraldine "Bubby" Litvin Shaffer's 100th birthday.
8 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
9 Resolution to Senator Karen Berg for presentation.
